            <title>[LU-2026] MDT kernel panic: Kernel BUG at fs/jbd2/transaction.c:292 RIP  [&lt;ffffffff887aae03&gt;] :jbd2:jbd2_journal_start+0x3a/0xdf</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2026</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We had an MDT kernel panic recently. We were able to get a partial core file and from that get the crash log. It managed to kernel panic in a really weird spot. I have asked them to verify that the hardware is solid as there are some messages in the mcelog file. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the meantime, can someone take a look at the log and see if it makes any sense?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
