&lt;p&gt;Also can you elaborate more on how that might cause an oops in the jbd2 code? What are the chances of another oops? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="45555" author="bobijam" created="Wed, 26 Sep 2012 02:51:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;lock enqueue handling upon resource 1993378622/164683178 was never finished (kept on sleeping in ldlm_expired_completion_wait) and stopped accepting client&apos;s reconnection. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Cannot tell why MDS could not finished the lock handling though (it was waiting for the lock&apos;s grant or cancellation finished before moving forward).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
